  <h3>Cryptography</h3>


  <div class="row">
      <p class="descriptionBody col s8 offset-s2">
        <b>Cryptography</b> is the fusion of security engineering and mathematics.
        It refers to the science and art of designing ciphers.
        A <b>cryptographer</b> is a person who uses and design ciphers.
        <b>Cryptanalysis</b> is the science and art of breaking these ciphers and
        A <b>cryptanalyst</b> is a person who can hack secret codes and read other people’s encrypted messages.
        A cryptanalyst can do hack an encrypted message by identifying patterns in the message, in order
        to be produce a decryption algorithm or simply find general weakness in an encryption algorithm,
        without necessarily having intercepted the actual message.
        Cryptanalysts are also called <b>hackers</b>.
      </p>
